AIIMS project  , collecting data, helping patients, fact based approach, rigorous data collection= gathered and analyzed, accuracy and filtering, understood the needs, inteviewed doctors, nurses, researched possible mathematical models or solutions, brainstormed, developed recommendations, worked intensively with the staff

